title: Failure to enforce any provision of the Terms of Service does not constitute a waiver of such provision
quoteText: Conditions shall be deemed a further or continuing waiver of such term or any other term, and a party's failure to assert any right or provision under these Terms of Use shall not constitute a waiver of such right or provision.
